# HWAX Portal — PROD routing destinations.   Format:  <system-id>=<URL>
# Same format as routes.env, but the address each service is reachable at in prod.
# Selected in prod via ROUTES_PATH=config/routes.prod.env (see .env.real).
# Uncomment + set each as the platform goes live; omitted = tile stays "coming_soon".
#
# Each value is whatever the destination is actually reachable at (see routes.env header
# for the full "which URL?" guide). Services can be ANYWHERE:
#   another server by IP   :  heax-hub=http://10.123.45.67:4180
#   its own domain         :  heax-hub=https://heax.sec.samsung.net
#   same host as the portal:  heax-hub=http://localhost:4180
# After editing:  ./infra/scripts/restart.sh

# heax-hub=https://heax.sec.samsung.net
# ai-data-hub=https://aidata.sec.samsung.net
# mx-white-paper=https://mxwp.sec.samsung.net
# report-archive=https://report.sec.samsung.net
# smart-twin-cluster=https://twin.sec.samsung.net
# spdm=https://spdm.sec.samsung.net
